<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-badge">The AI-Native Patient Operating System</div>
  <h1>
    The smartest healthcare companies<br />don't build infrastructure.<br
    />They build on <em>ours.</em>
  </h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">
    Compliant cloud. Core workflows. AI agents that automate scheduling, intake,
    routing, and the operational burden MCOs have carried for decades — while
    most companies are still figuring out where AI fits. PatientOS is what the
    best companies wish they'd had from day one.
  </p>
  <div class="hero-actions">
    <a href="#cta" class="btn-primary">Request a Demo</a>
    <a href="#solution" class="btn-secondary">See How It Works</a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 8rem 2rem 6rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .hero::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: -20%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 800px;
    height: 800px;
    background: radial-gradient(
      circle,
      rgba(62, 232, 181, 0.06) 0%,
      transparent 70%
    );
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(62, 232, 181, 0.2);
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    background: var(--accent-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    font-weight: 500;
    animation: fadeInDown 0.8s ease-out;
  }

  .hero-badge::before {
    content: "";
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: pulse 2s infinite;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-family: "DM Serif Display", serif;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 6.5vw, 5.5rem);
    line-height: 1.05;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.2s both;
  }

  .hero h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2vw, 1.35rem);
    color: var(--text-dim);
    max-width: 680px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.4s both;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.6s both;
  }

  @media (max-width: 968px) {
    .hero {
      padding: 7rem 1.5rem 4rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .hero-actions {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }
  }
</style>
